eu.focusnet.app.model

Class AppContentInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.focusnet.app.model.AbstractInstance
      • eu.focusnet.app.model.AppContentInstance

  • public class AppContentInstance
extends AbstractInstance
    This object contains the whole content of the application (projects, pages, widgets). It is based on a corresponding AppContentTemplate and the content is resolved iteratively to obtain each part of the application with a proper data context.
